Album: ProcessArtiste: SamphaGenre: Dance, Electronic, Alternative R&amp;BRelease: February 3"Process" is Sampha's debut album. It is a expressive and emotional piece that details things the artist has been through, which include the loss of his parents. Essential tracks on the 10-track album include Plastic 100&deg;C, Blood On Me, Kora Sings, Timmy's Prayer, Incomplete Kisses and What Shouldn't I Be? Sampha has impressive vocal ability which makes his music what it is &mdash; unique. "Process" is a brilliant, well-crafted, fascinating debut. It indicates that the British singer still has a lot to offer. Star rating: 4/5